  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lulu Way is a 30 min brain-teaser, room-based puzzle game about Lulu the little astronaut trying to escape space! It features simple gameplay mechanics but with interesting original puzzle designs </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lulu moves in anti-clockwise, constantly</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lulu can only jump from one block to another block</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lulu must make its way to the next room by jumping onto the right blocks, choose your blocks carefully!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*** 50 amazing hand-crafted levels await you, help Lulu out! ***</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Lulu running in circles while you plan your next jump</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/104c6a7099ca9378c688154f67cf0986.poster.avif?t=1773646542\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/104c6a7099ca9378c688154f67cf0986.webm?t=1773646542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/104c6a7099ca9378c688154f67cf0986.mp4?t=1773646542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Lulu making a daring jump from one block to another</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/533019608e1e59348452fe8a209fffb3.poster.avif?t=1773646542\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/533019608e1e59348452fe8a209fffb3.webm?t=1773646542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/533019608e1e59348452fe8a209fffb3.mp4?t=1773646542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Lulu collects a key!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/861df198b0cbfd9fb9b9d52fa8c3d96e.poster.avif?t=1773646542\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/861df198b0cbfd9fb9b9d52fa8c3d96e.webm?t=1773646542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/861df198b0cbfd9fb9b9d52fa8c3d96e.mp4?t=1773646542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Lulu makes a U-turn!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/c1105a48c6ee9a12659960227b704072.poster.avif?t=1773646542\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/c1105a48c6ee9a12659960227b704072.webm?t=1773646542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/c1105a48c6ee9a12659960227b704072.mp4?t=1773646542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Lulu gets eaten by Glooby the red monster</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/f2eb77beb2c6b6719717a374452acc38.poster.avif?t=1773646542\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/f2eb77beb2c6b6719717a374452acc38.webm?t=1773646542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897990/extras/f2eb77beb2c6b6719717a374452acc38.mp4?t=1773646542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
